{"tid":1416124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你班廢柴真係好撚好笑","createTime":"2019-08-05T14:38:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T16:41:38.000Z","uid":33736,"like":98,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"e468073169f1656c71f5c85679cfabf731a6943a","tid":1416124,"uid":33736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:38:41.000Z","msg":"林鄭將光復香港時代革命講成挑戰主權、搞革命<br />\n你班友就縮哂沙<br />\n驚喇唔再講喇<br />\n然後用乜嘢失焦、民意為藉口<br />\n掩飾自己嘅懦弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命呢句口號<br />\n從一開始就係對港共政權嘅挑戰<br />\n唔好唔記得梁天琦係主張香港獨立<br />\n如果你哋唔同意、冇覺悟<br />\n唔該由一開始就咪撚跟風嗌呢句口號<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為你班友唔撚配</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"ef0c2315931d437ab644be273829836a1cb903cc","tid":1416124,"uid":275634,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:40:13.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<br />\n係要同共產黨鬥 吹咩<br />\n睇下邊個死得快d <br />\n大不了攬炒<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6127d0489c8d32b1bf2d9e5665684d6cad867a0","tid":1416124,"uid":222189,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:40:17.000Z","msg":"事實係好多人唔配叫呢句口號喎<br />\n呢句口號2019年後我冇叫過<br />\n今次拎出黎用都係借屍還魂但冇哂內在精髓"},{"pid":"344a6fcd6da639ef63dcfb97ee692944cd9c230d","tid":1416124,"uid":265622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:43:41.000Z","msg":"呢個得<br />\n而家最緊要比d新活動和理非參加<br />\n遊行示威衝突射彈都射到慣射到疲倦"},{"pid":"1d059a69ec1e7617b3f3bd689ad320178ec2851d","tid":1416124,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:44